{"tid":1924734,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「哈利波特」Daniel Radcliffe 親自否認確診武漢肺炎：sorry囉我成日都一個病人樣","createTime":"2020-03-14T00:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T04:22:20.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2221cd34f05e09356ed1a5552c789f78a63572","tid":1924734,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T00:39:58.000Z","msg":"昨日奧斯卡影帝湯姆漢克斯（Tom Hanks）夫婦、NBA 爵士隊兩名球員確診新冠肺炎，讓外界不禁驚嚇連連。然而，日前傳聞也中鏢的「哈利波特」男星丹尼爾雷德克里夫（Daniel Radcliffe）在風波延燒數日後，親自發聲否認假消息，玩笑表示會有此傳聞是因為他總是一副生病樣。<br />\n<br />\n日前一個冒充「英國廣播公司突發新聞」的推特帳號發文指出，丹尼爾雷德克里夫的新冠肺炎檢測呈現陽性。貼文一出讓不少網友轉發分享，讓人誤以為這位童星出身的英國男星真的感染了新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n隨後，此帳號因違反規則，不僅是造謠貼文被刪除，整個推特也遭到停用。<br />\n<br />\n而他本人則在昨日接受澳洲電台節目《Smallzy&rsquo;s Surgery》的訪問中聊到此事，透露當時為了舞台劇進行梳妝時，他的化妝師跟他說：「我侄子傳訊息給我，跟我說你得到冠狀病毒耶。」讓他超困惑，於是對方拿了那則推特的貼文給他看。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n丹尼爾雷德克里夫說道：「貼文上面寫著丹尼爾雷德克里夫是第一個確診冠狀病毒的知名人士。我想這是因為我看起來總是一副生病的樣子。」非常蒼白的臉龐讓別人鎖定他為目標，讓造謠可信度大大提升。<br />\n<br />\n現年 30 歲的丹尼爾雷德克里夫在《哈利波特》系列電影完結後，轉向參演多部獨立製作影片，最新作品為驚悚電影《逃離普勒托利亞》（Escape From Pretoria）以及《奇蹟締造者》（Miracle Workers）第二季。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n先前曾有小道消息指出他將主演漫威美劇《月光騎士》（暫譯，Moon Knight），但他在上月底已親自闢謠，表明對那項目完全一無所知。（EW）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/tw/article/%E8%A2%AB%E5%82%B3%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8C%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E6%B3%A2%E7%89%B9%E3%80%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%98%B2%E8%92%BC%E7%99%BD%E8%87%89%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%89%AF%E7%94%9F%E7%97%85%E6%A8%A3%E5%95%A6-D9klR8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Ftw%2Farticle%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25EF%25BC%2581%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2593%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%2589%25B9%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%2598%25B2%25E8%2592%25BC%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%2587%2589%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2589%25AF%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E5%2595%25A6-D9klR8&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=919f306c\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/tw/article/%E8%A2%AB%E5%82%B3%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8C%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E6%B3%A2%E7%89%B9%E3%80%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%98%B2%E8%92%BC%E7%99%BD%E8%87%89%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%89%AF%E7%94%9F%E7%97%85%E6%A8%A3%E5%95%A6-D9klR8</a>"},{"pid":"869c8a97aeb5023b69104db952ad3c02141faa17","tid":1924734,"uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVD5OJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVD5OJL.jpg&h=c237f9af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"978fc96378d00fcf58f56096c61fa4936ad1ad8f","tid":1924734,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"869c8a97aeb5023b69104db952ad3c02141faa17","tid":1924734,"uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVD5OJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVD5OJL.jpg&h=c237f9af&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T00:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4801133fa052701f4202e1b6d9fee11ca3ab80","tid":1924734,"uid":5406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21a3eab71373f570582fe62b9cbb61f23d264cf","tid":1924734,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"d6ec8de3ae4a7c20194397a3b56dad30d99a21e1","tid":1924734,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote